experiences.subtitle: Clipit
workDescription: Developed a bookmark saving browser extension that helped users save time and avoid clutter. Used Firebase and Chrome Storage API, reducing bookmark retrieval time by 50% through local storage optimization. Leveraged NLP and TensorFlow models to generate 70% accurate summaries and tags based on user input data. Implemented real-time synchronization between local storage and Firebase, minimizing data redundancy and improving performance.
